{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-01423/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-01423"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:14:23"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A waitress smiles at a man offscreen."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-01423","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-01423"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1/84ca2cfb-e068-4191-ba3e-932e4cd45461","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T20:29:09.775Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In contrast to Henrietta’s “yes” during her fitting and in keeping with Alma's rebellious nature, one of her first words to Reynolds is “no.” Unlike so many in his life, Alma will be more than willing to defy Reynolds.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:17.84671532846712,44.04744525547443,233.56204379562055,152.23357664233586"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1/7b5ee9d4-0e4b-4e50-ab3f-6c972806b3c0","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T20:29:20.066Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma responds with surprise to Reynolds’s request for “some sausages.” On the one hand, she is simply taken aback by how much he intends to eat. On the other hand, given the sexual tension throughout their exchange and the upcoming appearance of the breakfast plate itself, there may be more to her shock.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:22.12773722627734,224.77007299270076,230.1350364963504,149.67153284671542"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1/6cc7760c-21d8-4835-995a-6f0347c7ddae","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T20:29:35.461Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Beyond the dynamic of a sitting diner and a standing server, Alma hovers over Reynolds with a faint smile while he looks at her adoringly, which foreshadows the film’s final plot point that reveals a reversal of the power dynamic between the characters: since the beginning, this shot seems to tell us, Alma is in control. However, the eye-level yet slightly high-angle shot draws out the tension between Alma as a submissive figure and her future role as a more dominant one.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01423/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:481.3467153284672,39.021897810218995,1192.817518248175,985.0072992700731"}}}]}]}]}